Unsloth
================================================================================

Training scripts in `training/` are designed for the Unsloth stack
(https://github.com/unslothai/unsloth). Unsloth is used under its respective
open-source license. If you redistribute Unsloth-derived training artifacts,
follow Unsloth's license and attribution requirements.

================================================================================
E2B (Gemma 4 edge variant)
================================================================================

We target **Gemma 4 E2B** (`unsloth/gemma-4-E2B-it`) for laptop/edge QLoRA
training. "E2B" refers to Google's Gemma 4 edge sizing nomenclature, not the
E2B sandbox company. No affiliation implied.

